## 🌍 Environment Variables

- `NEXT_PUBLIC_` prefix = exposed to browser — only for truly public values
- Server-only secrets: no `NEXT_PUBLIC_` prefix, never reference in client files
- Always define in `.env.local` (dev) and Vercel dashboard (prod)
- Never hardcode secrets or API keys in source code
- Access via `process.env.VAR_NAME` — never destructure at module level for server vars

---

## 🚀 Vercel Deployment

- Default runtime is Node.js — specify `export const runtime = 'edge'` only when intentional (and ensure all dependencies are Edge-compatible)
- Keep Serverless Functions small — avoid large dependencies in API routes
- Use `next/image` for ALL images — never raw `<img>` tags (breaks optimization + LCP)
- Set proper `cache` options on `fetch()` calls for ISR behavior
- Use Vercel environment variables, not `.env` files in production

---

## 🔒 Security

- Always sanitize and validate user input server-side (Zod)
- Never expose internal error details to clients — log server-side, return generic messages
- Use Supabase RLS as the primary data access control layer
- CSRF is handled by Same-Site cookies — use Server Actions for mutations (not GET requests)
- Rate-limit sensitive API routes (use Upstash or Vercel middleware)

---

## ♻️ Code Style

- Max file length: 200 lines — split into smaller modules if exceeded
- One exported component per file
- Async/await only — no `.then()/.catch()` chains
- Early returns over nested if-blocks
- Named exports for components, default export allowed for page files only
- Avoid barrel files (`index.ts`) for large modules — they hurt tree-shaking

---

## 🚫 Anti-patterns to Avoid

| ❌ Don't | ✅ Do instead |
|---|---|
| `'use client'` on layouts | Keep layouts as Server Components |
| `useEffect` for data fetching | Fetch in Server Components |
| `getSession()` for auth checks | `getUser()` on server |
| `select('*')` on Supabase | Explicit column selection |
| `any` type | `unknown` + type narrowing |
| Raw `<img>` | `next/image` |
| Secrets with `NEXT_PUBLIC_` | Server-only env vars |
| Inline `style={{}}` | Tailwind utilities |
| Try/catch swallowing errors silently | Log + rethrow or return error |
| `createClient` from supabase-js | `@supabase/ssr` clients |
